[Course_Description]
Recruiting talented candidates via social channels has become an important part of a recruiter's job. But how does one best tackle this channel? In this course, instructor Bert Verdonck shares strategies that can help recruiters efficiently and successfully recruit top talent on social platforms. Bert explains how social recruiting fits into the overall recruiting process, which social platforms to focus on, and how to jump-start your social media recruiting presence. He also shares how to find and approach ideal candidates, collaborate with hiring managers, and drive referral recruitment.